cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use turboquant-cli in your research, please also cite the underlying
  TurboQuant, PolarQuant, and QJL papers listed under references.
type: software
title: turboquant-cli
abstract: >-
  Cross-platform CLI for local LLM inference using quantized models, with
  TurboQuant, PolarQuant, and QJL KV cache compression methodologies.
authors:
  - alias: ithllc
url: https://github.com/tqcli/tqcli
repository-code: https://github.com/tqcli/tqcli
license: Apache-2.0
keywords:
  - llm
  - quantization
  - kv-cache
  - inference
  - turboquant
  - polarquant
  - qjl
